{"tid":354524,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"宇宙巨G.E.M.機開慈善個唱 9歲Celine紅館騷受阻？","createTime":"2017-08-10T13:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T10:24:09.000Z","uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d12ea73eb59b33ec0a38551de50f1473ac526e9a","tid":354524,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"9歲小巨肺Celine(譚芷昀)參加《全美一叮》(America's Got Talent)一唱成名。上集更喺節目中，成為首個華人奪得Gloden Buzzer獎。(新聞連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2hqqlcn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2hqqlcn&d=ZmXSrbDKmsQzFN1FCt4cqpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7136ee5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2hqqlcn</a>)<br />\n<br />\n年僅9歲就蜚聲國際，比起另一巨肺宇宙巨G.E.M.更勁。Celine經理人蕭定一日前就即刻公布年尾會同Celine喺紅館開演唱會，仲話呢個演唱會係慈善用途，希望可以打破當年19歲G.E.M.，成為最年輕藝人喺紅館開騷紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n雖然蕭定一諗法正面樂觀理想，不過今日有報道指Celine申請紅館檔期未獲審批，蕭定一如意算盤未必打得響。其實蕭定一之前都有話過紅館檔期好難申請，加上申請手續繁複，若能喺今年底或明年初成事已經係個奇迹。同時，之前同Celine爸譚順生有軱轕嘅家燕媽媽，都有透露阿女試過幫佢申請紅館開騷，但最後都係不獲審批。"},{"pid":"dc25eadf4284acd78778f58b7d0d6ce74e0bd2c7","tid":354524,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:06:20.000Z","msg":"算唔算童工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b82ec558a8549fe3a9ab960808cd06ea7ff5ec","tid":354524,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:44:53.000Z","msg":"有咩人會去睇"},{"pid":"3fa5b78cb952ebf7f9c8b78dd9882ce4f3587f26","tid":354524,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好俾佢開 難聽到痺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893f8437d7e794c941dc010d0514fc2932aae9e8","tid":354524,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:43:17.000Z","msg":"兩舊屎"},{"pid":"0b7f9ffca6b440d25901daf1cbec5425c57fbd1d","tid":354524,"uid":40433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"1993年5月6日：台灣歌手林志穎以17歲之齡成為紅館最小年紀開個唱的歌手。"}]}